## Educational Use Notice

This software is designed for educational purposes to teach neural network 
concepts through interactive gameplay. While the MIT license allows commercial 
use, we encourage educational institutions, teachers, and students to use this 
software freely for learning and teaching purposes.

## Attribution

If you use this software in an educational context, academic paper, or 
derivative work, we would appreciate attribution to:

